version_description: First version of the chords to "I Don't Mind" by Phantom Planet. The song is a simple 4 chord structure.

From Phantom Planet's self titled album (2004). Tab based off of: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NH7q2XQrUEU These chords should be accurate to both the acoustic and CD version. Note that the tempo is slower in the acoustic version.
Simplified version without power chords. Enjoy.

This is my first tab, so it probably has a few mistakes. I love the Phantom Planet version of this song and the "Crosby, Stills, and Nash" version on UG was slightly inaccurate and in a different key, so I decided to make the first Phantom Planet version on UG. I made it by ear, so I assume there will be some wrong chords, but it sounds pretty accurate overall.
This version is complete, and now includes section headers for the different sections of the song.
